      "content": "For high-stakes corporate settings, a polished and conservative appearance is key to projecting authority. Men should opt for classic, well-tailored suits in dark, solid colors, ensuring their grooming is impeccable—think neat haircuts and minimal, subtle grooming products. Women should favor sharp, well-fitting business attire, keeping makeup professional and hair styled in a controlled manner. The goal is to look effortlessly competent, suggesting that your focus is entirely on the business at hand.",
